---
const { title } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="welcome">
  <h1>Welcome to {title}!</h1>
  <p>We are thrilled to have you here. Our website is dedicated to providing you with the best content and resources on various topics.</p>
  
  <h2>What We Offer</h2>
  <p>Explore our wide range of articles, tutorials, and projects. Whether you are looking for the latest news, in-depth guides, or inspiration for your next project, we have something for everyone.</p>
  
  <h2>Get Started</h2>
  <p>To get started, check out our <a href="/projects">Projects</a> and <a href="/blog">Blog</a> sections. We hope you find our content valuable and engaging.</p>
</section>

<style>
  .welcome {
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  .welcome h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .welcome h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .welcome p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .welcome a {
    color: #007acc;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .welcome a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>